sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant FE as Miniapp
    participant Lend as lending-service
    participant Wallet as Connected Wallet
    participant AVAX as Avalanche
    participant DB as DB Gateway (optional)

    Note over FE,Lend: JWT already obtained from auth-service

    FE->>Lend: GET /benqi/markets
    Lend-->>FE: markets[]

    FE->>Lend: GET /benqi/account/:address/positions (Authorization header)
    Lend-->>FE: liquidity + normalized positions[]

    alt Supply/Borrow/Withdraw/Repay action
        FE->>Lend: POST /benqi-validation/validateAnd<Action> { amountWei, qTokenAddress }
        alt Validation contract configured
            Lend-->>FE: { validation tx, action tx, summary }
        else Validation fallback path
            Lend-->>FE: { action tx only, validationBypassed:true }
        end

        loop sequential execution
            FE->>Wallet: sendTransaction(preparedTx)
            Wallet-->>FE: txHash
            FE->>AVAX: wait/poll receipt(txHash)
            AVAX-->>FE: confirmed | reverted | timeout
        end

        opt DB gateway sync enabled
            Lend->>DB: sync markets/positions/tx metadata
        end

        FE->>Lend: GET /benqi/account/:address/positions
        Lend-->>FE: refreshed positions
        FE->>Lend: GET /benqi/account/:address/history and /snapshots
    end

